OL,3,CTata Steel's timeline for greener
OL,4,Csteelmaking in Port Talbot
OL,6,FPlans to shift from using blast
OL,7,Ffurnaces to an electric arc furnace
OL,8,Fwere announced in January.
OL,10,FReasons behind the decision include
OL,11,Foffsetting financial losses, as well
OL,12,Fas a commitment to producing steel in
OL,13,Fa more environmentally friendly way to
OL,14,Freduce CO2 emission.
OL,16,FThe restructuring will see 2500 jobs
OL,17,Flost across the UK plus an additional
OL,18,F300 in 3 years time. Around 1,900 of
OL,19,Fthose are jobs in Port Talbot.
