OL,6,FThe majority are expected to have left
OL,7,Fthe steelworks by the end of December,
OL,8,Fwith smaller numbers leaving by the
OL,9,Fend of March.
OL,11,FUnion voices, as well as those in the
OL,12,Fcommunity, have called the decision 'a
OL,13,Ftragedy'.
