OL,6,FA consultation phase is currently
OL,7,Funderway, with people being encouraged
OL,8,Fto ask questions and share feedback on
OL,9,Fthe electric arc furnace proposals up
OL,10,Funtil 15 October.
OL,12,FThe steel giant says they will be
OL,13,Fworking closely with authorities to
OL,14,Fapply for planning approvals by
OL,15,FNovember.
OL,17,FLarge scale site work on the furnace
OL,18,Fis expected to begin in Port Talbot in
