OL,6,FThe electric arc furnace is expected
OL,7,Fto be operational within three years
OL,8,Faccording to the company.
OL,10,FThe company says this #1.25 billion
OL,11,Fproject will be the largest investment
OL,12,Fin the UK steel industry for decades.
OL,14,FWhat is an electric arc furnace?
OL,16,FAn electric arc furnace produces steel
OL,17,Fdifferently than the more traditional
OL,18,Fblast furnace. It is filled with cold
OL,19,Frecycled steel. Electrodes are then
OL,20,Flowered into the furnace.
