OL,6,FWhy is Tata moving to greener
OL,7,Fsteelmaking?
OL,9,FThe company confirmed that previous
OL,10,Foperations were leaving them with
OL,11,Ffinancial losses totalling at around
OL,12,F#551 million during the last quarter
OL,13,Fof 2023.
OL,15,FThey had previously claimed losses of
OL,16,Fup to #1m a day. They claimed that
OL,17,Fsince acquiring the UK steel business
OL,18,Ffrom Corus in 2007, it had lost over
OL,19,F#4bn.
