OL,4,Csteelmaking in Port Talbot
OL,6,FThe shift towards an electric arc
OL,7,Ffurnace will aim to make operations
OL,8,Fmore financially viable.
OL,10,FTata Steel has also set a zero carbon
OL,11,Femission target, and they say the move
OL,12,Fto an electric arc furnace will get
OL,13,Fthem there, as the decision will
OL,14,Freduce the UK's entire industrial
OL,15,Fcarbon emissions by 8% and Port
OL,16,FTalbot's by 90%, according to the
OL,17,Fcompany.
